{"tid":264250,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"神能否創造一間無仆街的戲院","createTime":"2017-05-30T16:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T17:09:19.000Z","uid":38222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca7888a442d375f0416a5a29719f7a6dcd99e4d","tid":264250,"uid":38222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"近幾個月開始多大片上畫<br />\n但好多時入到場已經被班仆街搞到無癮<br />\n<br />\n老中青排名不分先後<br />\n聽/覆 voice msg <br />\n不停unlock睇電話 <br />\n同隔離位瘋狂討論/傾計<br />\n紙/膠袋聲 <br />\n<br />\n利申 <br />\n我遇到就 一噓 二屌出聲<br />\n好多時都會識做自動收皮<br />\n但咁樣真係無癮<br />\n自律大約兩個小時真係咁難咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時真係寧願睇早場 少人啲<br />\n其他場次多人 遇仆街的機會就高啲"},{"pid":"ad2fa17b601a0dbeb01cacea7077ee5015f47e50","tid":264250,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"最煩就係殊人個d仆街，搞到成個場嘈哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a12e46ed2726712475d3669682c5ccd6a9e4b8","tid":264250,"uid":38222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最煩就係殊人個d仆街，搞到成個場嘈哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪頭先傾計個仆街呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3115591b58d6e8a563ac9e4b57514db9db04d27","tid":264250,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"去豪華試過兩次有仆街冚家剷嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef726419c85501180a13e6a990a8376f778f1596","tid":264250,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最煩就係殊人個d仆街，搞到成個場嘈哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2838d17cce6d214d09a83b2ce5d4a79d0923bea","tid":264250,"uid":78039,"like":0,